<subSubSection box="[198,1422,1765,1792]" pageId="3" pageNumber="29" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,966,1792]" box="[198,1422,1765,1792]" pageId="3" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,1765,1791]" pageId="3" pageNumber="29">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name refers to the Southern Antarctic Ocean where the species was discovered.
</paragraph>
